first take a pan 
and add 2 tbs of oil 
and let it heat in low flame 
and now take 1 onion and chop it in small pices 
and now take the egg and break it and pour it in a bowl
and now add 1/2 tbs of salt and 1/2 tbs of chilli powder
and now  take the chopped onion and add it in the egg 
and stir it well 
and add that mixture in the pan 
and let it bake 
after 2 min you can see your omletis ready


now enjoy the your omlet .....